The time for war is NOW. Look around you, see the elves, standing there, smiling, giggling, playing.<br>
<br>
They are becomming more and more relaxed, as we become stronger.<br>
<br>
The time to strike them down is now. <br>
Do not be fooled, for we are at war.<br>
<br>
Among our collective of evil, we have many of those that stand in the way of an evil assult against of all that is light.<br>
<br>
These traitors stand in the way of our domination of the world, and stand to help and assist the lightbringers in every way needed.<br>
<br>
I have the names of two such traitors..<br>
One being Xyndrii. A Darkelven ShadowKnight that seems to enjoy assisting light bringing Gnomes in gaining a good fighting experence.<br>
The other being Cassimus, a Darkelven Mage who thinks that it is fun to help Halfling Druids slay our guards.<br>
<br>
Both of them have been marked for death, as will all traitors that have completly fallen from the Way which is defined for all that bring Shadows, Hate, War, and Death into the world.<br>
<br>
Their is never an excuse for assisting the lightbringers, less the lightbringer is ready to have its sprit turned into the way of Darkness.<br>
<br>
Then, the approiate tests will be given so that this lightbringer can prove his loyality to the Darkness.<br>
<br>
All those that dare turn their back on the Path will gain a death far far worse then what I could give to any Highelven piece of Trash.<br>
<br>
For the Highelf had no choice in being born weak.<br>
<br>
These traitors become weak, when they could of been powerful.<br>
<br>
